エントランスへの移動場所3

parameters: Clea: Of course, Caron is not here...

Thief Nora: Absolutely, it's with the dragon! It's the
rooftop where the dragon escaped to!

Imperial Dark Division: By the order of Caron-sama, anyone
other than the Dragon Slayer shall be killed.
Captain Clevo: ...I see, then they're our enemies.
Thief Nora: Yes! I'm glad the captain is safe too!
Clea: Nora-san, you really managed to defeat Clevo-san...

Captain Clevo: It's a difference in feelings. I had already
lost in my heart from the beginning.

Captain Clevo: I tried infiltrating the upper floor, but the
quality of the dark division is clearly different. We should
be cautious.

Thief Nora: Captain, let's go together! Today is not just
the Emma Mercenary Corps, but the revival of the Emma Thief
Corps!

Captain Clevo: The revival of the Emma Thief Corps... Let's
bring along our fallen comrades as well.

\CL Nora has acquired the support skill Proud Dual Swords
\C[0] and can now use it \|.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

King Rex: I apologize for the strict security measures, but
I believe that now is the most dangerous time.
Clea: I think it's a natural decision.

King Rex: It seems that some nobles intend to support the
second prince. Both the second prince and General Atu have
disappeared from the palace...

King Rex: The details of continued cooperation for security
will be discussed by the guild leader.

King Rex: Now, onto the main topic. I believe that all of
you are the greatest contributors.

King Rex: Caron cornered and defeated the dragon, saving
many citizens of the empire. Truly deserving to be called a
hero.
Clea: That's too kind of you to say.

King Rex: Although Caron has been given the title of Dragon
Slayer, we will revoke it and give her a new title from us.

King Rex: Due to the unprecedented achievements that deserve
titles for others as well, we will hold a separate ceremony
to confer them at a later date.
Clea: It is an honor beyond what I deserve, King Rex.

King Rex: I apologize for repeating myself, but your
achievements are unprecedented, so I want to repay you in
advance for what I can do.

King Rex: While I cannot grant any wish... I want to
consider fulfilling your hopes to the best of my ability.

Mage Relm: Then, may I share? In this journey, I lost my
dream and gained a new one.

Mage Relm: That is to become an Archmage of the Magic
Academy.

Thief Nora: I want to make the Emma Mercenary Corps bigger!
I want to help people in need and those who have nowhere to
go.
Thief Nora: Also, I want to repay the people who helped me!

Priestess Sophia: I carry many sins, but from now on, I will
confront them and walk the path of a priestess.

Priestess Sophia: Under the guidance of Sister Eleo, my
mentor.

King Rex: Everything is difficult, especially when it comes
to interfering with the Magic Academy, even for a king--

Clea: King Rex, this is a declaration of determination. It's
not something I want someone else to fulfill, but something
I will fulfill myself.

Clea: We have learned that wishes are something we must
seize with our own hands.
Clea: While I am deeply grateful, I respectfully decline.

King Rex: I apologize for saying something insensitive.
That's why you are the heroes who defeated the dragon.
King Rex: ...May I hear the other person's wish?

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: I... am a weak human.
That's why I want to work for the sake of those who are also
weak.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: Thank you for your
consideration, King Rex-sama.

Young Rex: Thank you for telling me. With this, I can become
a king without hesitation, Alicia-san.

King Rex: Originally, this would be a banquet, but we hold
it when awarding achievements.

King Rex: Finally, let me express my gratitude once again. I
will not let your sacrifice be in vain.
King Rex: I promise to become that kind of king.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

King Rex: Mobilize the civil servants who will reform the
organizational structure within the royal palace and have
them handle this matter!

\CL 【King Rex's Aftermath】The transition from the Caron
regime was carried out swiftly and recognized by the elders.
A preparation period of seven years was set, and the Third
Tarasa War was implemented.

\CL Showing talent beyond that of a father, he realized the
long-cherished desire of the empire, the Tarasa merger. As a
result, he was called the Conqueror King, the Hero King, and
was widely loved by the people.

\CL In his personal life, he was blessed with both sons and
daughters, with the son becoming the successor.

\CL However, after the death of King Rex, King Leval, who
harbored madness, was born after three generations.

\CL After a long civil war, the imperial monarchy came to an
end and transitioned into a republic. The position of king
was avoided, but Rex left his name in the history of the
empire as the ideal king.

Royal Palace Civil Servant Emoni: Organizing the documents
from the Caron regime... Yes, and also making contact with
the Caron faction in the Senate!

\CL 【Emoni, the Royal Palace Civil Servant's Aftermath】Emoni
provided King Rex with all the information regarding the
dark side of the Caron regime and his role as a civil
servant. Recognizing her dedicated work, she was granted
amnesty in exchange for her dismissal.

\CL Afterwards, I struggled with whether to return to the
Adventurer's Guild or choose to go back to my hometown. I
decided to return home and assist my father and brothers
with their work, making a significant contribution to the
expansion of our business.

\CL Throughout her life, she never missed visiting the grave
of the great widow and Agonia.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
